Package: quicklm
Title: Quick Checks and Visualizations for Linear Models
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Hasbany",
           family = "James",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jhasbany@calpoly.edu"),
    person(given = "Bodwin",
           family = "Kelly",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "kelly@bodwin.us"))
Description: Simple functions for checking and visualizing linear model assumptions. Allows the user to simlutaneously test many variables for model inclusion, and provides simple and clear output.  Plots residuals against many variables, and checks normality.
